Logical Model: Diagnostic laboratory results

Official URL: http://example.org/StructureDefinition/DiagnosticLaboratoryResults Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2024-12-18 Computable Name: DiagnosticLaboratoryResults

Captures diagnostic test results along with sample information to determine TB infection status.

Usage:

  • Use this Logical Model Profile: TB Case Surveillance
